parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power steering system can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The power steering becomes stiff or hard to turn
especially at low speeds; the steering wheel may lock up or become difficult to turn when making turns or parking; the vehicle may vibrate or shake when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the steering rack can cause the vehicle to become difficult to steer, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The steering becomes stiff or hard to turn
especially at low speeds; the steering wheel may lock up or become difficult to turn when making turns or parking; the vehicle may vibrate or shake when turning.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission and engine performance can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power when driving; the transmission shifts erratically or hesitates; the engine misfires or runs rough; the vehicle may vibrate or shake when driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the stabilization and traction control systems can cause the vehicle to lose traction or stability, increasing the risk of accidents or loss of control.
symptoms: The vehicle's traction control and stability systems malfunction or fail; the vehicle may lose traction or stability when driving; the vehicle may vibrate or shake when driving.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to lose power, hesitate, or stall, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to shift gears
loses power
or stalls; the transmission slips or fails to engage; the vehicle shakes or vibrates; the RPMs increase without acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch wave plate can cause the transmission to slip or fail, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle hesitates to shift gears
loses power
or stalls; the transmission slips or fails to engage; the vehicle shakes or vibrates; the RPMs increase without acceleration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ECM can cause the vehicle to shut down or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle shuts down or loses power; the engine light comes on; the vehicle experiences electrical issues.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, or catch fire, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine shuts down or loses power; the engine light comes on; the vehicle experiences engine noise or vibration.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the Stabilitrak and traction control systems can cause the vehicle to lose control, leading to accidents.
symptoms: The Stabilitrak and traction control warning lights come on; the vehicle experiences loss of control or stability.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the wiring and electrical systems can cause the vehicle to experience electrical issues, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle experiences electrical issues; the wiring is damaged or corroded; the vehicle's systems malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various warning lights to illuminate, including the airbag, service engine, and low beam headlights, which can lead to a loss of safety features and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: Warning lights illuminate
burning odor near the front of the vehicle
airbags fail to deploy
and electrical system shorts.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch and transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, and make it difficult to shift gears, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
clutch pedal sticks to the floor
vehicle stalls
loss of power
and difficulty shifting gears.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The engine misfires and stalling can cause the vehicle to lose power, stall, and potentially cause accidents.
symptoms: Engine misfires
vehicle stalls
loss of power
and difficulty starting the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the headlights can cause reduced visibility, which can lead to accidents.
symptoms: Headlights fail to function
headlight bulbs burn out frequently
and difficulty replacing headlight bulbs.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the lift gate and trunk can cause injury and make it difficult to access the trunk area.
symptoms: Lift gate falls without warning
lift gate hits occupants
and difficulty accessing the trunk area.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the tire pressure monitoring system can cause reduced safety and potentially lead to accidents.
symptoms: Tire pressure monitoring system warning light illuminates
and difficulty diagnosing and repairing the issue.
